parameters:
Inn: Welcome, hello. The price for one
night here is 5 Rill, would you like to
stay?
Inn: We look forward to your next visit.

Inn: It seems you don't have enough
money...

Inn: Welcome, hello. Please note that
our inn does not accommodate naked
guests.

Traveler: I came to Logres to become a
clergyman. I hope I pass the
interview...

Traveler: I have decided to give up the
path of a clergyman. I will return to
the empire.

Dancer: The girl in this room...? Well,
I haven't seen her.

Dancer: I wonder if she went back to her
hometown?

Traveler: W-What happened!? Are you
being forced to do something terrible!?

Dancer: ...Could it be that walking
around naked is a trend in this town?

By talking to the innkeeper, you can
move to the flashback room.
